## Description {#details}

Declarations for ObjC runtime functions and constants.

These are initialized lazily to avoid cluttering up the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module">Module</a> with unused declarations.

Definition at line 52 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/objcarc/arcruntimeentrypoints-h">ARCRuntimeEntryPoints.h</a>.
